findings.title: Agreement for Consulting Services
findings.summary: Consultant agrees to provide Python coding services to Client in exchange for Rs 50,000 upon completion. The agreement includes confidentiality and governing law provisions.
bullets: Python coding services provided by Consultant to Client
Client agrees to pay Rs 50,000 upon completion of services
Either party may terminate with 24 hours notice
Consultant shall keep all proprietary data confidential forever
This agreement is governed by the laws of Mauritius
actions: Client should review the terms and conditions
Both parties should sign the agreement for it to be binding
Client should provide the payment upon completion of services
Consultant should ensure all proprietary data is kept confidential
risks: Risk of breach of confidentiality by Consultant
Risks associated with the interpretation and enforcement of Mauritian law
